sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant F as Founder
    participant CLI as kipi CLI
    participant SK as Skeleton repo<br/>~/projects/kipi-system
    participant REG as instance-registry.json
    participant I1 as ktlyst-strategy
    participant I2 as 4_points_consulting
    participant IN as ...all N instances

    F->>CLI: kipi update
    CLI->>REG: load instance list
    REG-->>CLI: 18 registered instances
    CLI->>SK: read latest skeleton state
    SK-->>CLI: q-system, .claude/rules, .claude/agents,<br/>.claude/output-styles, plugins

    par parallel rsync per instance
        CLI->>I1: copy q-system subset
        CLI->>I1: copy .claude/rules
        CLI->>I1: copy .claude/agents
        CLI->>I1: copy plugins
        CLI->>I2: same
        CLI->>IN: same
    end

    CLI->>F: report changed files per instance

    Note over CLI,IN: Root CLAUDE.md does NOT sync.<br/>Only q-system/CLAUDE.md, rules,<br/>agents, output-styles, plugins<br/>propagate via kipi update.

    F->>CLI: kipi push (from an instance)
    CLI->>SK: detect generic improvements
    CLI->>F: present diff for skeleton merge
